description: Yooma Wellness Inc. engages in the manufacturing, marketing, distribution, and sale of wellness products in Canada, the United States, Europe, and Asia. Its wellness products include hemp seed oil, and hemp-derived and cannabinoid (CBD) ingredients. The company sells its products through various platforms, such as ecommerce, mass-market retail, and independent retail partners. Yooma Wellness Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
